Secure Smart Cam Transfer (SSCXfer) is a fairly brutal fork
of the Vidiom app. It has been paired down to just be
a multi-path uploader, to which we are adding Tor/Orbot,
SQLCipher db encryption and throttling support.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

